SIFAX Group organized its first Bring A Child To Work Day yesterday to commemorate the International Children’s Day Celebration. The children that attended the event had the opportunity to interact with staff at the Ports & Cargo Terminal. John Jenkins, our Managing Director, was also on ground to receive and welcome the children. John Jenkins, Managing Director, Ports & Cargo Handling Services Limited (middle) with staff children during the SIFAX Group Children’s Day Celebration which was held yesterday at the Ports & Cargo Terminal, Tin-Can Island, Lagos. (Middle)- Olumuyiwa Akande, Corporate Affairs Manager, SIFAX Group and Mrs. Kehinde Odunaiya, Assistant Manager, Human Resources, SIFAX Off Dock Nigeria Limited, cutting the cake to celebrate children’s day organized by SIFAX Group at the Ports & Cargo Terminal, yesterday.